data.persona: I am a man and woman. I am a subject of the king and harvest food for the village. I have two children and work to feed them. I hope they do not have to fight any wars.
data.description:
You are in the Castle Kitchen.
The castle kitchen is gigantic! There are racks and racks filled with ingredients for enough food to feed the castle every day. Ten long wooden tables take up much of the room. Along the wall are cooking instruments of every type as well as huge ovens to cook the food.
There's a rack, a cooking instrument, a spice, a huge oven, a room, a serving platter, a wall, an a trash bin, a cooking instruments of every type, an ingredient, a table, and a salt here.
The person and the butler are here.

You are carrying a bag, and wielding a knife.
